statements: SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE id = 10;
SELECT page_url, timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE visitor_id = 100;
SELECT visitor_id, engagement_score FROM website_traffic WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, page_url, timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE engagement_score > 0.5 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT visitor_id, AVG(engagement_score) AS avg_score FROM website_traffic GROUP BY visitor_id;
SELECT page_url, engagement_score FROM website_traffic WHERE visitor_id = 100 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE engagement_score > 7.5 AND timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31'
SELECT AVG(engagement_score) AS avg_score, COUNT(DISTINCT visitor_id) AS unique_visitors FROM website_traffic GROUP BY page_url HAVING COUNT(visitor_id) > 5
SELECT page_url, MAX(engagement_score) AS max_score FROM website_traffic WHERE timestamp >= '2022-06-01' GROUP BY page_url ORDER BY max_score DESC
SELECT visitor_id, COUNT(*) AS visits FROM website_traffic WHERE engagement_score < 5 GROUP BY visitor_id ORDER BY visits DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_count DESC;
SELECT page_url, visit_count FROM website_traffic WHERE time_spent > 10;
SELECT id, page_url, time_spent FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_count < 100 ORDER BY time_spent ASC;
SELECT user_id, username, engagement_score FROM user_engagement WHERE engagement_score >= 80;
SELECT username, email FROM user_engagement WHERE last_login BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_count > 100 ORDER BY time_spent DESC
SELECT page_url, visit_count FROM website_traffic WHERE time_spent < 10.5
SELECT username, email FROM user_engagement WHERE last_login > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY username ASC
SELECT page_url, time_spent FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_count BETWEEN 50 AND 100
SELECT user_id, engagement_score FROM user_engagement WHERE engagement_score > 75
SELECT * FROM website_visits WHERE user_id = 123
SELECT user_id, page_visited, duration_seconds FROM website_visits ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT source_name, referral_link, traffic_count FROM traffic_sources WHERE traffic_count > 1000 ORDER BY traffic_count ASC
SELECT user_id, unique_visits, interactions FROM user_engagement WHERE interactions >= 5
SELECT page_visited, COUNT(visit_id) AS visit_count FROM website_visits GROUP BY page_visited
SELECT visit_id, user_id, timestamp, page_visited, duration_seconds FROM website_visits WHERE user_id = 5 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, timestamp, page_visited FROM website_visits WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp <= '2022-01-31' ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT SUM(duration_seconds) AS total_duration FROM website_visits WHERE user_id = 3;
SELECT source_name, SUM(traffic_count) AS total_traffic FROM traffic_sources GROUP BY source_name HAVING total_traffic > 1000 ORDER BY total_traffic DESC;

SELECT w.user_id, w.page_visited, u.total_duration_seconds, t.source_name FROM website_visits w JOIN user_engagement u ON w.user_id = u.user_id JOIN traffic_sources t ON w.user_id = t.source_id WHERE u.total_duration_seconds >= 3600 AND t.traffic_count > 500 ORDER BY u.total_duration_seconds DESC, t.traffic_count DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM WebsiteVisits;
SELECT user_id, page_id, visit_timestamp FROM WebsiteVisits WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT username, email FROM UserMetrics WHERE registration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT page_name, visit_count FROM PageMetrics ORDER BY visit_count DESC;
SELECT source_name, traffic_type, traffic_date FROM TrafficSources WHERE traffic_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01';
SELECT * FROM WebsiteVisits ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(visit_id) AS total_visits FROM WebsiteVisits GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY total_visits DESC;
SELECT username, email, last_login FROM UserMetrics WHERE registration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT page_name, visit_count, like_count FROM PageMetrics WHERE like_count > 100 ORDER BY visit_count DESC;
SELECT source_name, COUNT(source_id) AS total_sources FROM TrafficSources GROUP BY source_name HAVING total_sources > 5 ORDER BY total_sources DESC;
SELECT * FROM visitor_info WHERE browser_used = 'Chrome';
SELECT visitor_name, location FROM visitor_info ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT engagement_id, visitor_id, engagement_timestamp FROM user_engagement WHERE engagement_type = 'click';
SELECT * FROM website_visits WHERE time_spent_seconds < 60;
SELECT source_name, total_visits, conversion_rate FROM referral_sources WHERE total_visits > 100 ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_visits ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT visitor_name, browser_used, location FROM visitor_info WHERE device_type = 'Desktop'
SELECT page_visited, time_spent_seconds FROM website_visits WHERE visit_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' ORDER BY time_spent_seconds DESC
SELECT source_name, total_visits, conversion_rate FROM referral_sources WHERE total_visits > 1000 AND conversion_rate > 0.2
SELECT visitor_name, browser_used, location FROM visitor_info WHERE location LIKE '%USA%'
